      About this item

      • Pick Colors from Camera: Take a picture or keep camera focusing to choose a color applying to your bluetooth light bulb. CRI ≥ 90 to restore the true color of the surrounding environment.
      • Sync Your Music: Personalize your Govee multicolor bulbs with more than 16 million colors and a monochrome palette. Our smart bulb lights can change colors according to rhythm of music. Dynamic or soft rhythm, depending on your preferences.
      • Connect via Bluetooth & App Control: Via Bluetooth connect the LED Light Bulb with the "Govee Home" App. Group control can control up to multi rgb light bulbs at the same time
      • Timer & Wake-up Modes: Set your color changing LED bulbs to turn on/off at a specific time. Especially use the “Sunrise” mode to make the color lights bulb brighten to help you wake up, use the “Sunset” mode lets the bulbs darken to help you sleep.
      • Energy Saving: The brightness of this 7W LED bulb is equivalent to a 60 watt incandescent, saving you 90% on lighting costs.
      • Bluetooth direct control, don't support Alexa or Google Assistant "Govee Home" App is required

      Product Description

      Personalize your Govee RGB light

      • Our smart bulb light can change colors according to rhythm of music melody.
      • You can choose dynamic rhythm or soft rhythm, depending on your preferences or the music you are playing.

      Timer & Wake-up

      • Use the “Sunrise” mode to make the bulb light brighten to help you wake up, use the “Sunset” mode lets the bulb light darken to extinguish to help you sleep.

      8 Scene Modes

      • You can set different scene modes on Govee App to match various occasions including kitchen, living room, bedroom. LED Bluetooth light bulb also can be used for table lamp, cafe, bar, party, etc.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      5 out of 5 stars
      The BEST LED Lightbulb!
      I bought this LED Lightbulb in hopes to replace my old lightbulb that had burnt out and I'm going to be honest... I'm super surprised.The Lightbulb is bright and vibrant with color, the app/customizations are absolutely amazing and I have to give props to Govee where it's deserved, the app is SUPER user friendly and straight forward, just download the app, make an account, go to devices, click the plus sign in the top right corner, select the product you bought (In my case it was the H6001 LED Lightbulb), it'll search for a Bluetooth device nearby and BOOM, it's connected and you can change the color, brightness or other various settings to whatever you like, weather that be Red, Orange, Yellow, Green, Blue, Purple or any other color that you desire because they have a color wheel to choose that EXACT color you want, not to mention but this lightbulb actually has not affected my electricity bill at all, if anything it lowered it from my previous lightbulb, Govee seems to NEVER fail on product quality or customer service!Oh and here's some tips/troubleshooting for anyone having some various questions!- When searching for your device in the Govee Home app, ensure the lightbulb is fully screwed in and on like you would do with a normal lightbulb, I was confused at first because I just screwed the light bulb in and forgot to turn on my stand to actually give it power, after I turned it on, it found my lightbulb instantly!- Make sure you have Bluetooth on, the lightbulb won't work without it!- If you're wondering why the "White" is pink-ish/not bright, below in the app on your device where you select colors there's a bar labeled with "Warm White" and "Cold White" turn it all the way to "Cold White" and it'll be SUPER bright and be a full white color.If you're still having issues after these such as your lightbulb isn't being recognized in the app or your having other various problems, Govee offers a "Rapid Replacement" that can be found under the profile tab or you can contact them via their website (govee.com/support) and find more help there!Overall, I think this LED/RGB Lightbulb is really solid and well worth the price after 2 months of use and I will keep everyone updated if anything happens in the next month's (8/14/22).

        4.0 out of 5 stars very good option without of led lights
        Reviewed in the United States on October 11, 2024
        Verified Purchase
        Review of Govee LED Light Bulb
        The Govee LED Light Bulb is a feature-packed option for those looking to enhance their home lighting, but it comes with a few caveats. Here’s a detailed look at its performance and functionality.

        Design and Installation
        This A19 bulb fits seamlessly into most standard fixtures. Installation is straightforward—simply screw it in and connect via the Govee app using Bluetooth. No hub is required, making setup quick and easy.

        Smart Features
        The music sync capability is a standout feature, allowing the bulb to change colors and pulse with ambient sounds. While this can create a fun atmosphere for parties or movie nights, users should note that the bulb can emit a noticeable humming or buzzing sound when in use, especially at lower brightness levels.

        Dimming and Color Options
        The Govee LED bulb offers adjustable brightness and a wide array of colors, allowing for personalized lighting to match your mood. The app provides various preset scenes and scheduling options for added convenience.

        Connectivity Limitations
        One downside is that the bulb does not support Google Home or other major smart home platforms. This means you’ll need to rely solely on the Govee app for control, which may limit integration with other smart devices in your home.

        Energy Efficiency
        With a power rating of 7W (equivalent to a 60W incandescent bulb), this LED bulb is energy-efficient, helping you save on electricity bills while maintaining good brightness.

        Value
        Considering its features, including the vibrant color options and music sync, the Govee LED Light Bulb still offers solid value. However, the noise and lack of broader smart home integration are worth keeping in mind.

        Conclusion
        Overall, the Govee LED Light Bulb is a versatile choice for enhancing your lighting experience, especially with its music sync feature. However, potential buyers should consider the humming noise and the lack of Google Home compatibility. If you're looking for fun lighting effects and don’t mind using the Govee app, this bulb can be a great addition to your home!
